<translation id="4033006861724039519">Ingobo yomlando yesifaki imoshekile noma ayivumelekile. Sicela ulande i-Ecosia futhi.</translation>
<translation id="1026101648481255140">Qalisa Kabusha Ukufaka</translation>
<translation id="8296565077892323223">Enza ngendlela oyifisayo uphinde ulawule i-Ecosia. Isibuyekezo siyatholakala.</translation>
<translation id="2804130178228362015">Kunesofthiwe eyingozi kwikhompyutha yakho. I-Ecosia ingayisusa, ibuyise izilungiselelo zakho, futhi ikhubaze izandiso ukwenza isiphequluli sakho sisebenze kahle futhi.</translation>
<translation id="1065672644894730302">Okuncamelayo kwakho akukwazi ukufundwa.

Ezinye izici kungenzeka zingabi khona futhi izinguquko kokuncamelayo ngeke zize zilondolozwe.</translation>
<translation id="8055222671516987714"><ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS"/> ngaphambilini ibikade isebenzisa i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2000339487270823788">Lena yi-Ecosia yakho</translation>
<translation id="8078678931242443254">Ubani osebenzisa i-Ecosia?</translation>
<translation id="6346154190168496057">Ayikwazi ukubuyekeza i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="1152920704813762236">Mayelana ne-ChromeOS</translation>
<translation id="7303930050538184306">&amp;Vula ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="1203500561924088507">Siyabonga ngokufaka. Kufanele uqale kabusha ibhrawuza yakho ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-<ph name="BUNDLE_NAME"/>.</translation>
<translation id="6650631555168164414">Ungajabulela okuningi ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="1523806373970723624">Qalisa kabusha ukuze ubuyekeze i-&amp;Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5279514147510747661">Sicela ulinde ngenkathi i-Ecosia ifaka izibuyekezo zesistimu zakamuva.</translation>
<translation id="3117430309053294381">I-<ph name="MANAGER"/> idinga ukuthi ufunde uphinde wamukele Imigomo Yesevisi elandelayo ngaphambi kokusebenzisa le divayisi. Le migomo ayinwebeki, ayiguquki, noma ayikhawuleli Imigomo ye-EcosiaOS Flex.</translation>
<translation id="8067423333018528301">I-EcosiaOS ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngenxa yephutha lokungena ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="2926455547526018397">I-beta ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2995860351618948435">Le khompyutha isivele inenguqulo yakamuva ye-Ecosia. Uma isofthiwe ingasebenzi, sicela ukhiphe i-Ecosia uphinde uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="824192326282906244">Ungashintsha umqondo wakho noma kunini kumasethingi we-Ecosia. Izivivinyo zisebenza eduze kwendlela yamanje yokulethwa kwezikhangiso, ngakho ngeke ubone izinguquko ngokushesha.</translation>
<translation id="4696685525015809740">Izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Ecosia Canary</translation>
<translation id="3697186779259384993">Yenza ngendlela oyifisayo iphrofayela yakho entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="4062366803229254216">I-Ecosia idinga ukufinyelela kwe-Bluetooth ukuze iqhubeke 
 nokumatanisa. <ph name="IDS_BLUETOOTH_DEVICE_CHOOSER_AUTHORIZE_BLUETOOTH_LINK"/></translation>
<translation id="2441303983090031276">I-EcosiaOS Flex yenzeka ngenxa <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>yesofthiwe yomthombo ovulekile eyengeziwe<ph name="END_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>.</translation>
<translation id="5598074261782651109">Buyekeza i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="847970842635669371">U-<ph name="EXISTING_USER"/> usengenile ngemvume kakade kule phrofayela ye-Ecosia. Lokhu kuzodalela u-<ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS"/> iphrofayela entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="4943938785458240142">I-Ecosia isebenzisa ikhamela yakho.</translation>
<translation id="1936361330890313940">I-<ph name="FILE_NAME"/> iyingozi, ngakho-ke i-Ecosia iyivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="1597911401261118146">Ukuze uhlole uma ngabe amaphasiwedi akho aphephile kusukela ekuphulweni kwedatha nakwezinye izinkinga zokuvikela, <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>ngena ngemvume ku-<ph name="END_LINK"/>.</translation>
<translation id="5591151834004774364">I-Ecosia ivimbele leli fayela lengobo yomlando ngoba ingase ifihle uhlelo olungayilungele ikhompyutha</translation>
<translation id="1597547208646178091">Ukuze kwenziwe i-Ecosia iphephile, sikhubaza isandiso esilandelayo esingafakiwe kuhlu ku-<ph name="IDS_EXTENSION_WEB_STORE_TITLE"/> futhi kungenzeka singezwe ngaphandle kolwazi lakho.</translation>
<translation id="5875641815673321623"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD"/>Ungayiphatha kanjani idatha yakho:<ph name="END_BOLD"/> Ukuze sivikele ubumfihlo bakho, sisula ngokuzenzakalelayo izintshisekelo zakho ezindala kunamaviki ama-4. Njengoba uqhubeka nokubhrawuza, intshisekelo ingase ivele ohlwini futhi. Noma ungasusa izithakazelo ongafuni ukuthi i-Ecosia izicabangele.</translation>
<translation id="1628000112320670027">Thola usizo nge-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="1640672724030957280">Iyadawuniloda...</translation>
<translation id="1662146548738125461">Mayelana ne-ChromeOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="5500958820122281144">Vula isixhumanisi kuwindi le-Ecosia Inco&amp;gnito</translation>
<translation id="7602423871874451395">I-Ecosia ayikwazi ukufunda nokubhala kumkhombandlela wayo wedatha:

<ph name="USER_DATA_DIRECTORY"/></translation>
<translation id="1914619467562029368">{COUNT,plural, =1{Umlawuli wakho ulungiselele i-Ecosia ukuze ivaleke uma ingenzi lutho isikhathi esingaphezu komzuzu ongu-1.}one{Umlawuli wakho ulungiselele i-Ecosia ukuze ivaleke uma ingenzi lutho isikhathi esingaphezu kwemizuzu engu-#.}other{Umlawuli wakho ulungiselele i-Ecosia ukuze ivaleke uma ingenzi lutho isikhathi esingaphezu kwemizuzu engu-#.}}</translation>
<translation id="3939060118711873999">I-Ecosia isiphequluli sewebhu esisebenzisa amakhasi ewebhu nezinhlelo zokusebenza ezinejubane elikhulu kakhulu. Iyashesha, ayiguquki, futhi kulula ukuyisebenzisa. Dlulisa amehlo kuwebhu ngendlela ephephile nakakhulu ngokuvikelwa ku-malware nobugebengu bokweba imininingwane ebucayi okwakhelwe ku-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="6022879254514691681">{0,plural, =1{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha kwihora}one{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha emahoreni angu-#}other{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha emahoreni angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="4021894801595982809">I-Ecosia izolondoloza le phasiwedi ku-akhawunti yakho ye-Ecosia. Ngeke kudingeke ukuthi uyikhumbule.</translation>
<translation id="4811228173434336381">I-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2346323077583431428">Yenza isiqinisekiso sokuthi ungene ngemvume ku-Ecosia ku-<ph name="TARGET_DEVICE_NAME"/> yakho bese uzama ukuthumela futhi.</translation>
<translation id="1812689907177901597">Ngokuvala lokhu, ungangena ngemvume kumasayithi e-Google njenge-Gmail ngaphandle kokungena ngemvume ku-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="5055330219314726197">I-Ecosia idinga imvume yokufinyelela kukhamera yakho kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="1508200558303644420">I-Ecosia akusona isiphequluli sakho esizenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="8135642897811755229">I-beta yeEcosia (mDNS-In)</translation>
<translation id="7268098999602465369">I-Ecosia ingaphandle kwedethi</translation>
<translation id="1919130412786645364">Vumela ukungena ngemvume kwe-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="6235917057647038042">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-Ecosia, uzodinga i-macOS 10.13 noma eyakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-macOS 10.12.</translation>
<translation id="1953553007165777902">Iyadawuniloda... Kusele imizuzu engu-<ph name="MINUTE"/></translation>
<translation id="8608092457636055141">Iphrofayela ngalinye linolwazi lwayo lwe-Ecosia njengamabhukhimakhi, umlando, amaphasiwedi, nokuningi</translation>
<translation id="2018879682492276940">Ukufakwa kwehlulekile. Sicela uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="7375011918167125899">Enye i-akhawunti isivele ingene ngemvume. Ukuze uqhubeke nokuphequlula ngokwehlukile, i-Ecosia ingakwazi ukukudalela iphrofayela yakho.</translation>
<translation id="207902854391093810">Lapho imizamo ivuliwe, Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sivumela amasayithi owavakashelayo ukuba acele ulwazi ku-Chrome olusiza isayithi ukukala ukusebenza kwezikhangiso zawo. Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sikhawulela ukulandelela indawo yonke ngokudlulisa ulwazi oluncane ngangokunokwenzeka phakathi kwamasayithi.</translation>
<translation id="8655983536493871574">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-Ecosia, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 8.</translation>
<translation id="3590393640971125498">Imigomo ye-EcosiaOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="864244542982029641">Yekela i-Ecosia yize kunjalo?</translation>
<translation id="3791194915692553395">I-EcosiaOS Flex yenzeka <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>ngenxa yesofthiwe yomthombo ovulekile eyengeziwe<ph name="END_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>, njengoba kunjalo <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_LINUX_OSS"/>ngendawo yokuthuthukiswa kwe-Linux<ph name="END_LINK_LINUX_OSS"/>.</translation>
<translation id="2120620239521071941">Lokhu kuzosusa izinto ezingu-<ph name="ITEMS_COUNT"/> kusuka kule divayisi. kuze uthole idatha yakho emuva kwesikhathi, ngena ngemvume ku-Chrome njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL"/>.</translation>
<translation id="2159716220295742156">Qalisa kabusha ukuze Ubuyekeze i-&amp;Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2123055963409958220">Siza ukwenza i-Chrome ibengcono ngokubika <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>izilungiselelo zamanje<ph name="END_LINK"/></translation>
<translation id="2131230230468101642">Ukuze sivikele ubumfihlo bakho, sisula ngokuzenzakalelayo izintshisekelo zakho ezindala kunamaviki ama-4. Njengoba uqhubeka nokubhrawuza, intshisekelo ingase ivele ohlwini futhi. Noma ungasusa izithakazelo ongafuni ukuthi i-Chrome izicabangele.</translation>
<translation id="5404489723475681578">Qalisa kabusha i-EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="5982672133249369264">Sicela uqalise kabusha -Ecosia manje</translation>
<translation id="2174917724755363426">Ukufaka akuqediwe. Uqinisekile ufuna ukukhansela?</translation>
<translation id="223889379102603431">Ulwazi olumayelana nendlela i-Chrome ephatha ngayo izitifiketi zayo zempande</translation>
<translation id="4337034173783952373">Ukuze ufinyelele ezintweni zakho ze-browser ye-Ecosia kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho, ngena ngemvume, bese uvula ukuvumelanisa</translation>
<translation id="4735588186234302898">Okhiye be-Ecosia API abekho. Okunye ukusebenza kwe-Ecosia kuzokhutshazwa.</translation>
<translation id="7908111389403807005">Ingabe uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukukhipha i-Ecosia?</translation>
<translation id="2309047409763057870">Lokhu ukufakwa kwesibili kwe-Google Chrome, futhi akukwazi ukwenziwa isiphequluli sakho esizenzakalelayo.</translation>
<translation id="7613817989637275906">I-Ecosia ithole ukuthi lezi zandiso zinohlelo olungayilungele ikhompyutha:</translation>
<translation id="7273750863406285983">I-Ecosia idinga imvume ukuze ifinyelele kukhamera yakho nemakrofoni yaleli sayithi</translation>
<translation id="234869673307233423">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho. Zama futhi emuva kwesikhathi.</translation>
<translation id="5707346538075088068">Noma iyiphi idatha ye-Ecosia ekhiqizwa ngesikhathi sokusetshenziswa kwale phrofayela (efana nokudalwa kwamabhukhimakhi, umlando, amaphasiwedi, namanye amasethingi) ingasuswa umlawuli wephrofayela yomsebenzi. <ph name="LEARN_MORE"/></translation>
<translation id="2359808026110333948">Qhubeka</translation>
<translation id="3959732324458144441">Isistimu ye-EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="3632544319066562282">I-Ecosia ifuna ukuthumela amaphasiwedi akho. Thayipha iphasiwedi yakho ye-Windows ukuze uvumele lokhu.</translation>
<translation id="2485422356828889247">Khipha</translation>
<translation id="2534507159460261402">I-Google Pay (ikopishelwe ku-Chrome)</translation>
<translation id="2559253115192232574">Kamuva, isayithi olivakashelayo lingacela i-Chrome ukuthi ibone izintshisekelo zakho ukuze yenze izikhangiso ozibonayo ngokwezifiso zakho. I-Chrome ikwazi ukwabelana ngezintshisekelo ezifika ku-3.</translation>
<translation id="2563121210305478421">Qalisa kabusha i-Chrome?</translation>
<translation id="5824812022890208563">U-<ph name="EXISTING_USER"/> usengenile ngemvume kakade kule phrofayela ye-Ecosia. Ukuze uqhubeke nokuphequlula ngokwehlukile, i-Ecosia ingakwazi ukukudalela iphrofayela yakho.</translation>
<translation id="80155189677487610">Ayikwazi ukufaka inguqulo ye-Ecosia efana nalena esebenza manje. Sicela uvale i-Ecosia uphinde uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="2586406160782125153">Lokhu kuzosusa idatha yakho yokuphequlula kusukela kule divayisi. Ukuze uthole idatha yakho emuva kwesikhathi, ngena ngemvume ku-Chrome njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL"/>.</translation>
<translation id="6391863622742187823">Thola ibhrawuza yakho ye-Ecosia kusukela ku-<ph name="ACCOUNT_EMAIL"/></translation>
<translation id="2622559029861875898">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola izibuyekezo. Zama ukuhlola ukuxhumeka kwakho ku-inthanethi.</translation>
<translation id="1761341660094265938">I-EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="7774247008790177839">Vula isixhumanisi ku&amp;thebhu entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="9178613517891824246">Siza wenze i-Ecosia ibe ngcono ngokuthumela imibiko yokuphahlazeka ne-<ph name="UMA_LINK"/> ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="815199437159352723">Lesi sandiso siguqule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswa uma uqala i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="1676748966275099244">Isexwayiso: I-Ecosia ayikwazi ukuvimbela izandiso kusukela ekurekhodeni umlando wesiphequluli sakho. Ukuze ukhubaze lesi sandiso kumodi ye-incognito, yekisa ukukhetha le nketho.</translation>
<translation id="1831192335802727557">I-Ecosia idinga imvume ukuze ifinyelele kukhamera yakho kuleli sayithi</translation>
<translation id="2770231113462710648">Guqula isiphequluli esizenzakalelayo sibe yi-:</translation>
<translation id="2775140325783767197">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho. Zama ukuhlola ukuxhumeka kwakho ku-inthanethi.</translation>
<translation id="2799223571221894425">Qalisa kabusha</translation>
<translation id="2847461019998147611">Bonisa i-Google Chrome ngalolu limi</translation>
<translation id="8109744984354428711">Iqalisa i-Ecosia...</translation>
<translation id="812798451698099271">Iphrofayela ye-Ecosia enale akhawunti isikhona kakade</translation>
<translation id="2861074815332034794">Ibuyekeza i-Chrome (<ph name="PROGRESS_PERCENT"/>)</translation>
<translation id="727568860157522676">Ungene ngemvume ku-Ecosia!</translation>
<translation id="2885378588091291677">Isiphathi somsebenzi</translation>
<translation id="2888126860611144412">Mayelana ne-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="2915996080311180594">Qala Kabusha Ngemuva Kwesikhathi</translation>
<translation id="2926676257163822632">Amaphasiwedi angaqinile aqageleka kalula. Vumela i-Chrome <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>ikudalele futhi ikhumbule amaphasiwedi aqinile<ph name="END_LINK"/>.</translation>
<translation id="219546601381787154">I-Ecosia idinga imvume yekhamera kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="2928420929544864228">Ukufaka kuqedile.</translation>
<translation id="2929907241665500097">I-Chrome ayibuyekezekanga, kunokuthile okungahambanga kahle. <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>Lungisa izinkinga zokubuyekaza kwe-Chrome nezibuyekezo ezihlulekile.<ph name="END_LINK"/></translation>
<translation id="3907708440788567041"><ph name="PAGE_TITLE"/> - Inethiwekhi Yokungena ngemvume - i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5622643576877267490">Qalisa kabusha ukuze ubuyekeze i-&amp;EcosiaOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="303514781271618814">I-Chrome ihlola izakhi ezintsha ezivumela amasayithi ukuthi alethe ukuzizwisa kokubhrawuza okufanayo kusetshenziswa idatha yakho encane</translation>
<translation id="2234042158691635795">I-Ecosia ikumodi yangemuva.</translation>
<translation id="3038232873781883849">Ilinde ukufaka...</translation>
<translation id="3059710691562604940">Ukuphequlula okuphephile kuvaliwe. I-Chrome incoma ukuba kuvulwe.</translation>
<translation id="385080958066798123">Ithebhu le-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="3080151273017101988">Qhubeka nokusebenzisa izinhlelo zokusebenza zangemuva ngenkathi i-Google Chrome ivaliwe</translation>
<translation id="6876820794875877783">Kukhona inguqulo entsha, evikelekile ye-Ecosia etholakalayo.</translation>
<translation id="3100998948628680988">Qamba iphrofayela lakho le-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="3114643501466072395">Ukuze uhlole ukuba amanye amaphasiwedi akho aphephile yini kusukela ekuphulweni kwedatha nezinye izinkinga zezokuvikela, <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>ngena ngemvume ku-Chrome<ph name="END_LINK"/>.</translation>
<translation id="1722634673917783018">Izinguquko zakho zizosebenza ngesikhathi esilandelayo lapho uqalisa kabusha i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="2636091632287013185">Izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="7580831958727159171">Phakathi nezivivinyo, ungakwazi ukubona nokususa izihloko onentshisekelo kuzo ezisetshenziswa amasayithi ukuze uboniswe izikhangiso. I-Ecosia izolinganisa intshisekelo yakho ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wakamuva wokubhrawuza.</translation>
<translation id="2899530016847324742">{NUM_DEVICES,plural, =1{I-Ecosia ixhumeke kudivayisi ye-HID}one{I-Ecosia ixhunywe kumadivayisi we-HID}other{I-Ecosia ixhunywe kumadivayisi we-HID}}</translation>
<translation id="3245429137663807393">Uma futhi wabelana ngemibiko yokusetshenziswa kwe-Chrome, leyo mibiko ihlanganisa nama-URL owavakashelayo</translation>
<translation id="2388751143175762498">Ngena ngemvume ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="3286538390144397061">Qala kabusha manje</translation>
<translation id="9090890391337853620">Isisizi se-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5690368185132749068">{0,plural, =0{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha manje}=1{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kusekhondi elingu-1}one{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kumasekhondi angu-#}other{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kumasekhondi angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="7280797724682955539">Iphutha lesistimu yokusebenza livele ngesikhathi sokufakwa. Sicela ulande i-Ecosia futhi.</translation>
<translation id="2298752889004612764">Isilondolozi Senkumbulo Senze I-Ecosia Yashesha</translation>
<translation id="3428747202529429621">Kukugcina uphephile ku-Chrome futhi kungase kusetshenziswe ukuthuthukisa ukuvikeleka kwakho kwezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Google lapho ungene ngemvume</translation>
<translation id="3434246496373299699">I-Chrome ingahlola amaphasiwedi akho uma ungena ngemvume nge-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google</translation>
<translation id="1762318218111418450">Ingeza ku-Ecosia...</translation>
<translation id="6761747850241550887">Zingeze ngokwakho ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2149148292984034533">Imigomo ye-EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="3674955518940155608">Futhi sula idatha kusuka ku-Ecosia (<ph name="URL"/>)</translation>
<translation id="6558895515431832002">I-Ecosia idinga ukufinyelela kundawo yakho ukuze yabelane ngendawo yakho naleli sayithi</translation>
<translation id="3533694711092285624">Awekho amaphasiwedi alondoloziwe. I-Chrome ingahlola amaphasiwedi akho uma uwalondolozile.</translation>
<translation id="3541482654983822893">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho. Zama futhi emva kwamahora angu-24.</translation>
<translation id="8901409988302458368">Umlawuli wakho wesistimu ulungise i-Ecosia ukuvula esinye isiphequluli ikufinyelela i-<ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME"/>.</translation>
<translation id="3579965087968408543">Hlala usula idatha yesayithi kusukela kudivayisi yakho uma uvala i-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="7174674455569790401">Vumelanisa uphinde wenze kube ngeyakho i-Ecosia kumadivayisi akho onkana</translation>
<translation id="4933729908795930260">{COUNT,plural, =0{Umlawuli wakho udinga ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze kusetshenziswe isibuyekezo}=1{Umlawuli wakho udinga ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze usebenzise isibuyekezo. Iwindi lakho le-Incognito ngeke liphinde livuleke.}one{Umlawuli wakho udinga ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze usebenzise isibuyekezo. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}other{Umlawuli wakho udinga ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze usebenzise isibuyekezo. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}}</translation>
<translation id="464306605599005355">Manje sekulula ukusebenzisa i-Ecosia nge-Akhawunti yakho ye-Ecosia nakumakhompyutha abiwe.</translation>
<translation id="1490060441084292633">I-Ecosia ithole ukuthi i-"<ph name="EXTENSION_NAME"/>" inohlelo olungayilungele ikhompyutha</translation>
<translation id="5311911269004680646">I-EcosiaOS yenziwe ukuthi isebenze ngesofthiwe yomthombo ovulekile owengeziwe<ph name="BEGIN_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>isofthiwe yomthombo ovulekile<ph name="END_LINK_CROS_OSS"/>, njengoba kunjalo <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_LINUX_OSS"/>ngendawo yokuthuthukiswa kwe-Linux<ph name="END_LINK_LINUX_OSS"/>.</translation>
<translation id="3716540481907974026">Uhlobo lwe-ChromeOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="3718181793972440140">Lokhu kuzosusa into engu-1 kusuka kule divayisi. kuze uthole idatha yakho emuva kwesikhathi, ngena ngemvume ku-Chrome njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL"/>.</translation>
<translation id="9032120646440147804">Isandiso se-"<ph name="EXTENSION_NAME"/>" siguqule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswa uma uqala i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="3744202345691150878">Thola usizo nge-ChromeOS</translation>
<translation id="4600924482853773728">I-Ecosia - <ph name="PAGE_TITLE"/></translation>
<translation id="4969069484658032230">I-EcosiaOS Flex ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngenxa yephutha lokungena ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="1761341660094265938">I-EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="3952510753191144456">Lokhu kuzodalela u-<ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS"/> iphrofayela entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8534308095039131078">Sicela uvale wonke amawindi we-Ecosia bese uzama futhi.</translation>
<translation id="3865754807470779944">Inguqulo ye-Chrome i-<ph name="PRODUCT_VERSION"/> ifakiwe</translation>
<translation id="8283315171506895091">Vula isixhumanisi kuwindi le-Ecosia inco&amp;gnito</translation>
<translation id="6496553866814956056">Khipha i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="1118786556671181978">Ungabona futhi ususe izihloko zesayithi ongaba nentshisekelo kuzo ezisetshenziswa ukukubonisa izikhangiso. I-Ecosia izolinganisa ongaba nentshisekelo kukho ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wakamuva wokubhrawuza.</translation>
<translation id="8047394653992042491">I-EcosiaOS idinga ukuqaliswa kabusha ukuze yenze kusebenze isibuyekezo.</translation>
<translation id="4050175100176540509">Ukuthuthukiswa kokuphepha okubalulekile nezici ezintsha kuyathokala kunguqulo yakamuva.</translation>
<translation id="4817913198787198451">Yenza ngokwezifiso futhi lawula i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="3708834841667355707">I-Ecosia ihlola izakhi ezintsha ezivumela amasayithi ukuthi alethe ukuzizwisa kokubhrawuza okufanayo kusetshenziswa ulwazi lwakho oluncane</translation>
<translation id="319566061277127356">Setha iphrofayela yakho entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="7105712012505419722">Ungena ngemvume nge-akhawunti ephethwe futhi unikeza umlawuli wayo ukulawula okungaphezulu kwephrofayela yakho ye-Ecosia. Idatha yakho ye-Ecosia, efana nezinhlelo zokusebenza zakho, amabhukhimakhi, umlando, amaphasiwedi, nezinye izilungiselelo zizoboshezelwa ngonaphakade ku-<ph name="USER_NAME"/>. Uzokwazi ukususa le datha nge-Ecosia ama-Akhawunti we-Ideshibhodi, kodwa ngeke uze ukwazi ukuhlobanisa le datha nenye i-akhawunti. <ph name="LEARN_MORE"/></translation>
<translation id="4148957013307229264">Iyafaka...</translation>
<translation id="7691143774653486474">Isifaki sihlulekile ukungaminyanisi ingobo yomlando. Sicela ulande i-Ecosia futhi.</translation>
<translation id="6826163993811146231">{0,plural, =1{Qalisa kabusha i-Ecosia phakathi nosuku}one{Qalisa kabusha i-Ecosia phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-#}other{Qalisa kabusha i-Ecosia phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="4205939740494406371">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho. Zama futhi ngemva kwamahora angu-24 noma <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>hlola amaphasiwedi ku-akhawunti yakho ye-Google<ph name="END_LINK"/>.</translation>
<translation id="4222932583846282852">Iyakhansela...</translation>
<translation id="3554373328288278512">I-Ecosia idinga izimvume zekhamera nemakrofoni kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="424864128008805179">Phuma ngemvume ku-Chrome?</translation>
<translation id="8384922154025337808">Xhumanisa idatha yakho ye-Ecosia kule akhawunti?</translation>
<translation id="4565616259974605182"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD"/>Iyiphi idatha esetshenziswayo:<ph name="END_BOLD"/> Umlando wakho wokubhrawuza, irekhodi lamasayithi owavakashele usebenzisa i-Ecosia kule divayisi.</translation>
<translation id="4281844954008187215">Imigomo yesevisi</translation>
<translation id="4293420128516039005">Ngena ngemvume ukuze uvumelanise uphinde wenze kube ngeyakho i-Chrome kuwo onke amadivayisi akho</translation>
<translation id="6419542773162312746">Vumela isandiso ukuze ubonise izicelo zokufinyelela kubha yamathuluzi ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8864449561723972619">I-Ecosia Dev (mDNS-In)</translation>
<translation id="4334294535648607276">Ukulanda kuqedile.</translation>
<translation id="4335235004908507846">I-Chrome ingasiza ukukugcina uphephile kusukela ekuphulweni kwedatha, izandiso ezimbi, nokuningi</translation>
<translation id="2227704215309956084">I-<ph name="EXTENSION_NAME"/> ingezwe ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="4384570495110188418">I-Chrome ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho ngoba awungenanga ngemvume</translation>
<translation id="4427306783828095590">Isivikelo esithuthukisiwe senza okuningi ukuvimba ubugebengu bokweba imininingwane ebucayi kanye uhlelo olungayilungele ikhompyutha</translation>
<translation id="9035946286843935549">I-Ecosia - Inethiwekhi Yokungena ngemvume - <ph name="PAGE_TITLE"/></translation>
<translation id="6450895420388847775">Okunye ukusebenza ku-Ecosia kuyenzeka manje. Sicela uzame futhi emuva kwesikhathi.</translation>
<translation id="4459234553906210702">Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sivumela amasayithi owavakashelayo ukuba acele ulwazi ku-Chrome olusiza isayithi ukukala ukusebenza kwezikhangiso zawo. Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sikhawulela ukulandelela indawo yonke ngokudlulisa ulwazi oluncane ngangokunokwenzeka phakathi kwamasayithi.</translation>
<translation id="6107290018380796650">I-Ecosia ikuvumela ukuthi uchofoze inombolo yefoni kuwebhu bese wenza ikholi nge-Skype!</translation>
<translation id="4567424176335768812">Ungene ngemvume njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS"/>. Manje ungakwazi ukufinyelela amabhukhimakhi, umlando, nezinye izilungiselelo kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho ongene kuwo ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="6533266716128249922">Hamba kuzilungiselelo zesaziso se-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="488806616089631539">Uma i-Ecosia inokufinyelela, amawebhusayithi azokwazi ukukucela ukufinyelela.</translation>
<translation id="3268039966078382323">I-Ecosia ayikwazanga ukubuyekezela kwinguqulo yakamuva, ngakho-ke uyalahlekelwa kuzici ezintsha nokulungiswa kokuphepha.</translation>
<translation id="4690206707618474800">Okokuzikhethela: Siza ukuthuthukisa izakhi nokusebenza kwe-EcosiaOS Flex ngokuthumela ngokuzenzekelayo idatha yokuxilongwa nokusetshenziswa ku-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="9125443060066914183">Ukwenza i-Ecosia ivikeleke, sikhubaze ezinye izandiso ezingafakwanga kuhlu lwe-<ph name="IDS_EXTENSION_WEB_STORE_TITLE"/> futhi okungenzeka zifakwe ngaphandle kolwazi lakho.</translation>
<translation id="4680828127924988555">Khansela Ukufaka</translation>
<translation id="8236553889322631924">Izandiso, ama-app, namatimu asuka emithonjeni engaziwa angalimaza idivayisi yakho. I-Ecosia incoma ukuwafaka kuphela kusuka ku-Ecosia Web Store</translation>
<translation id="3305517118160815955">Ukufaka kuhlulekile ngenxa yephutha elingacacisiwe. Uma ngabe i-Ecosia isebenza okwamanje, sicela uyivale uphinde uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="4747730611090640388">I-Chrome ingalinganisela izintshisekelo zakho.  Kamuva, isayithi olivakashelayo lingacela i-Chrome ukuthi ibone izintshisekelo zakho ukuze yenze izikhangiso ozibonayo ngokwezifiso zakho.</translation>
<translation id="827222962844006655">I-Ecosia Canary (mDNS-In)</translation>
<translation id="2243562167758283214">Leli fayela lingaba yingozi, ngakho-ke i-Ecosia iyivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="3543284013834505767">Lokhu kusebenzisa isihloli sokupeleta esifanayo naleso esisetshenziswe kusesho lwe-Ecosia. Umbhalo owuthayiphayo kusiphequluli uthunyelwa ku-Ecosia. Ungahlala ushintsha le mpatho kuzilungiselelo.</translation>
<translation id="8144706290339578682">I-EcosiaOS Flex ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngoba Ukuvumelanisa akutholakali esizindeni sakho.</translation>
<translation id="4873783916118289636">Buyekeza izilawuli eziyinhloko zobumfihlo nokuvikeleka ku-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="8454595950895325762">Vumela i-Ecosia isebenze ngemuva</translation>
<translation id="489671036945006830">Vula isixhumanisi ku&amp;thebhu entsha ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5581150090232500900">Setha i-Ecosia njengesiphequluli sakho sokuzenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="6495878830719404098">Ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="6113625922434842626">I-EcosiaOS Flex ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngoba imininingwane yokungena ngemvume ku-akhawunti yakho iphelelwe isikhathi.</translation>
<translation id="4410570812343670816">Siyakwamukela kumaphrofayela we-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="4970880042055371251">Uhlobo lwe-ChromeOS</translation>
<translation id="796435732739009892">I-Ecosia ivimbe leli fayela ngoba lolu hlobo lwefayela luyingozi</translation>
<translation id="8570641140903702642">I-Canary ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="6718055545215052843">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-Ecosia, uzodinga i-macOS 10.13 noma eyakamuva. Le khompuyutha isebenzisa i-OS X 10.11.</translation>
<translation id="5098668839038261629">Lapho ivuliwe, uzophinde futhi uphume ngemvume ku-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="7782767522222146179">Thola izinhlelo zokusebenza ezinhle, amageyimu, izandiso namatimu e-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="6416551953415159186">Yenza ngokwezifiso iphrofayela yakho ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="1859120614572957305">Siyakwamukela ku-Ecosia; iwindi elisha lesiphequluli livuliwe</translation>
<translation id="6648664289472946060">Iphrofayela yakho ayikwazi ukusetshenziswa ngoba isuka kunguqulo entsha ye-Ecosia.

Ezinye izici kungenzeka zingatholakali. Sicela ucacise umkhombandlela wephrofayela ehlukile noma usebenzise inguqulo entsha ye-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="6960183526681645011">Uma wabelana ngedivayisi, abangane nomndeni bangaphequlula ngokwehlukile baphinde basethe i-Ecosia ngendlela abayifunayo.</translation>
<translation id="1869027055332251164">Izihambeli zingasebenzisa i-Ecosia ngaphandle kokushiya noma yini ngemuva.</translation>
<translation id="143614250230771428">I-EcosiaOS ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngoba ukuvumelanisa akutholakaleli isizinda sakho.</translation>
<translation id="1809194740315140401">I-Ecosia idinga imvume yokufinyelela kusitoreji ukuze idawunilode amafayela</translation>
<translation id="8975930032513941502">Ongakukhetha: Siza ekuthuthukiseni izakhi nokusebenza kwe-EcosiaOS ngokuthumela ngokuzenzekelayo idatha yokusetshenziswa neyokuxilonga ku-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="5357889879764279201">Thola usizo nge-ChromeOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="6665128960039431910">Iphinda ilawule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswayo uma uqala i-Ecosia noma usesho kusuka ku-Omnibox.</translation>
<translation id="1861504561909287316">Yabelana ngethebhu ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5412485296464121825">Amasayithi angagcina ulwazi nge-Chrome mayelana nezintshisekelo zakho. Ngokwesibonelo, uma uvakashela isayithi ukuze uthenge izicathulo zomjaho webanga elide, isayithi lingachaza intshisekelo yakho njengokugijima umjaho. Kamuva, uma uvakashela isayithi elihlukile ukuze ubhalisele umjaho, lelo sayithi lingakubonisa isikhangiso sezicathulo zokugijima ezisekelwe kuzintshisekelo zakho.</translation>
<translation id="6673288084648462613">Ifayela lakho lokuncamelayo limoshekile noma alivumelekile. 

I-Ecosia ayikwazi ukuthola izilungiselelo zakho.</translation>
<translation id="5524761631371622910">Uma izivivinyo zivuliwe futhi i-Chrome ikubeke ngokungahleliwe ekuzameni okusebenzayo, umlando wakho wokubhrawuza uthinta izikhangiso ozibonayo kanye nezinto ozithakaselayo njengoba kusikiselwa ngezansi. Ukuze ivikele ubumfihlo bakho, i-Chrome isula izintshisekelo zakho njalo ngenyanga.</translation>
<translation id="2905159584855395810">Yenza I-Ecosia Isheshe</translation>
<translation id="2549591663512786020">I-Ecosia izama ukubonisa amaphasiwedi.</translation>
<translation id="2470806471563820591">I-Ecosia (mDNS-In)</translation>
<translation id="3625533701824359646">I-<ph name="FILE_NAME"/> kungenzeka ibe ingozi, ngakho-ke i-Ecosia iyivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="3479730782477097349">{COUNT,plural, =0{Umlawuli wakho ucela ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze kusetshenziswe lesi sibuyekezo}=1{Umlawuli wakho ucela ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze kusetshenziswe lesi sibuyekezo. Iwindi lakho le-Incognito ngeke liphinde livuleke.}one{Umlawuli wakho ucela ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze kusetshenziswe lesi sibuyekezo. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}other{Umlawuli wakho ucela ukuthi uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia ukuze kusetshenziswe lesi sibuyekezo. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}}</translation>
<translation id="8544776492099331022">Yenza ngokwezifiso futhi lawula i-Ecosia. Okuthile kudinga ukuthi ukunake - chofoza ngemininingwane.</translation>
<translation id="4811228173434336381">I-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5789438819244101666">{SECONDS,plural, =1{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kusekhondi elingu-1}one{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kumasekhondi angu-#}other{I-Ecosia izoqala kabusha kumasekhondi angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="5727531838415286053">Uma i-Chrome ikubeke ngokungahleliwe esivivinyweni esisebenzayo, umlando wakho wokuphequlula uthinta izikhangiso ozibonayo kanye nezinto ozithakaselayo njengoba kusikiselwa ngezansi. Ukuze ivikele ubumfihlo bakho, i-Chrome isula izintshisekelo zakho njalo ngenyanga. Izintshisekelo ziyavuseleleka ngaphandle kwalapho uma uzisusa.</translation>
<translation id="5736850870166430177">Uma isayithi lizama ukuntshontsha iphasiwedi yakho, noma uma udawuniloda ifayela eliyingozi, i-Chrome ingathumela nama-URL, kuhlanganise nokuthile okuqukethwe kulelo khasi, Ekuphequluleni Okuphephile</translation>
<translation id="8301840715671593762">Iphrofayela ye-Ecosia enale akhawunti isikhona akakade kule divayisi</translation>
