<translation id="1318059253725731825">I-Ecosia isebenzisa imakrofoni yakho.</translation>
<translation id="8933665254023068908">Qalisa kabusha ukuze ubuyekeze i-&amp;EcosiaOS</translation>
<translation id="7311066525704006840">Isiphathi somsebenzi - i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="3212611709533299048">{COUNT,plural, =0{Isibuyekezo esisha se-Ecosia siyatholakala futhi sizosetshenziswa maduze ngemuva kokuthi uqalise kabusha.}=1{Isibuyekezo esisha se-Ecosia siyatholakala futhi sizosetshenziswa maduze ngemuva kokuthi uqalise kabusha. Iwindi lakho le-Incognito ngeke liphinde livuleke.}one{Isibuyekezo esisha se-Ecosia siyatholakala futhi sizosetshenziswa maduze ngemuva kokuthi uqalise kabusha. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}other{Isibuyekezo esisha se-Ecosia siyatholakala futhi sizosetshenziswa maduze ngemuva kokuthi uqalise kabusha. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}}</translation>
<translation id="7155997830309522122">Uma kunjalo, sicela uhlele iphasiwedi yakho elondoloziwe ku-Chrome ukuze ifane nephasiwedi yakho entsha.</translation>
<translation id="1027331268335328576">Siyakwamukela ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="675365189802108507">Ungafunda kabanzi mayelana nalezi zakhi kumasethingi we-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="4239392394637574967">Ungena ngemvume nge-akhawunti ephethwe futhi ukunikezela ukulawula kwayo ngaphezulu kwephrofayela yakho ye-Ecosia. Idatha yakho ye-Ecosia, efana nezinhlelo zakho zokusebenza, amabhukhimakhi, umlando, amaphasiwedi, nezinye izilungiselelo zizobophezeleka unaphakade ku-<ph name="USER_NAME"/>. Uzokwazi ukususa le datha nge-deshibhodi yama-akhawunti we-Ecosia, kodwa ngeke uze ukwazi ukuhlobanisa le datha nenye i-akhawunti. Ngokuzikhethela ungadala iphrofayela entsha ukuze ugcine idatha yakho ekhona ye-Ecosia ihlukanisiwe. <ph name="LEARN_MORE"/></translation>
<translation id="7295052994004373688">Lolu limi lusetshenziswe ukubonisa i-Google Chrome UI</translation>
<translation id="7296210096911315575">Ukusebenzisa okubalulekile nolwazi lokuphepha</translation>
<translation id="5549921590305750618">I-Ecosia idinga ukufinyelela kusitoreji ukuze ilande amafayela</translation>
<translation id="7339898014177206373">Iwindi elisha</translation>
<translation id="5337919616446681032">Uma ufuna ukusebenzisa le akhawunti kanye kuphela, ungasebenzisa Imodi Yesivakashi kwibhrawuza ye-Ecosia. Uma ufuna ukwengeza i-akhawunti yothile, <ph name="LINK_BEGIN"/>engeza umuntu omusha<ph name="LINK_END"/> ku-<ph name="DEVICE_TYPE"/> yakho.

Izimvume ozinikezile kakade amawebhusayithi nama-app zingase zisebenze kule akhawunti. Ungakwazi nokuphatha ama-Ecosia Account wakho kokuthi <ph name="SETTINGS_LINK_BEGIN"/>Amasethingi<ph name="SETTINGS_LINK_END"/>.</translation>
<translation id="2412381038247037703">Ubukade ungene ngemvume ku-Ecosia njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS"/>. Sicela usebenzise i-akhawunti efanayo ukuze uphinde ungene ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="5669097765101132299">I-Ecosia ivimbele leli fayela ngoba liyingozi</translation>
<translation id="3307959934543585795">I-Ecosia ingase ingasebenzi kahle ngoba ayisasekelwa kulokhu kusatshalaliswa kwe-Linux</translation>
