<translation id="1027331268335328576">Siyakwamukela ku-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8411844745163855310">I-<ph name="MANAGER"/> idinga ukuthi ufunde uphinde wamukele Imigomo Yesevisi elandelayo ngaphambi kokusebenzisa le divayisi. Le migomo ayinwebeki, ayiguquki, noma ikhawulela Imigomo ye-EcosiaOS.</translation>
<translation id="1263466865695943046">I-Ecosia ikuvumela ukuthi wazi uma amaphasiwedi akho afakwa engcupheni</translation>
<translation id="7158975242722498086">Umlawuli wakho wesistimu ulungiselele i-Ecosia ukuthi ivule i-<ph name="ALTERNATIVE_BROWSER_NAME"/> ukuze ifinyelele ku-<ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME"/>.</translation>
<translation id="7649070708921625228">Usizo</translation>
<translation id="93440396576488794">Ilogo yebhizinisi le-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="7655455401911432608">Umlando wakho wokubhrawuza, irekhodi lamasayithi owavakashele usebenzisa i-Chrome kule divayisi.</translation>
<translation id="7747138024166251722">Isifaki asikwazanga ukudala umkhombandlela wesikhashana. Sicela uhlolele isikhala esikhululekile sediski nemvume ukuze ufake isofthiwe.</translation>
<translation id="4871843754042758264">Chofoza igama lakho ukuze uvule i-Ecosia uphinde uqale ukudlulisa amehlo.</translation>
<translation id="2046160555506209000">Uma isithombe singenayo incazelo ephelele, i-Ecosia izozama ukukunikezela eyodwa. Ukuze udale izincazelo, izithombe zithunyelwa ku-Ecosia. Ungavala lokhu kuzilungiselelo noma kunini.</translation>
<translation id="8447746441670667471">Kukhona inguqulo entsha etholakalayo ye-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="5661123757512626239">I-Ecosia idinga imvume yendawo kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="7722016758804384514">Iphrofayela ibonakala isetshenziswa enye inqubo ye-Ecosia (<ph name="PROCESS_ID"/>) kwenye ikhompyutha (<ph name="HOST_NAME"/>).  I-Ecosia ikhiye iphrofayela ukuze ingamosheki. Uma uqinisekile ukuthi azikho ezinye izinqubo ezisebenzisa le phrofayela, ungavula iphrofayela uphinde uqalise kabusha i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="1047556320128249268">I-Ecosia izama ukukopisha amaphasiwedi. Thayipha amaphasiwedi akho e-Windows ukuze uvumele lokhu.</translation>
<translation id="4199684616787081033">Susa kusuka ku-Ecosia...</translation>
<translation id="2402290209407843024">Ukufakwa kuhlulekile ngenxa yephutha elingacacisiwe. Sicela ulande i-Ecosia futhi.</translation>
<translation id="7845233973568007926">Siyabonga ngokufaka. Kufanele uqalise kabusha ikhompyutha yakho ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-<ph name="BUNDLE_NAME"/>.</translation>
<translation id="7872446069773932638">Iyadawuniloda... kusele imizuzwana engu-<ph name="SECONDS"/></translation>
<translation id="2381210243314074423">Siyakwamukela ku-Ecosia, <ph name="ACCOUNT_FIRST_NAME"/></translation>
<translation id="6111519389633335269">Uma wabelana ngekhompyutha, abangani nomndeni bangadlulisa amehlo ngokuhlukene baphinde basethe i-Ecosia ngendlela nje abayifunayo.</translation>
<translation id="4727435569202742773">Umuntu othile ngaphambilini ungene ngemvume ku-Ecosia kule khompuyutha njengo-<ph name="ACCOUNT_EMAIL_LAST"/>. Sicela udale umsebenzisi omusha we-Ecosia ukuze ugcine ulwazi lwakho luhlukile.</translation>
<translation id="7917876797003313048">Ungaphatha ama-akhawunti we-Google wakho angene ngemvume. Ama-akhawunti wakho we-Google asetshenziselwe i-browser ye-Chrome, i-Play Store, i-Gmail, nokuningi. Uma ufuna ukungeza i-akhawunti yomuntu othile, njengelungu lomndeni, engeza umuntu omusha ku-<ph name="DEVICE_TYPE"/> yakho kunalokho. <ph name="LINK_BEGIN"/>Funda kabanzi<ph name="LINK_END"/></translation>
