<translation id="2838372953389311551">Uma isithombe singenayo incazelo ephelele, i-Ecosia izozama ukukunikezela eyodwa. Ukuze udale izincazelo, izithombe zithunyelwa ku-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="80471789339884597">Siyabonga ngokufaka. Kufanele uqalise kabusha wonke amabhrawuza akho ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-<ph name="BUNDLE_NAME"/>.</translation>
