<translation id="3216284932113164802">Habe! I-Ecosia iphahlazekile. Qalisa kabusha manje?</translation>
<translation id="8341646175450781745">Uma ivuliwe, i-Chrome ikhulula inkumbulo kumathebhu angasebenzi. Lokhu kunikeza amathebhu asebenzayo namanye ama-app izinsiza zekhompyutha ezengeziwe futhi kugcina i-Chrome ishesha. Amathebhu akho angasebenzi aphinde asebenze ngokuzenzakalelayo uma ubuyela kuwo. <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>Funda kabanzi<ph name="END_LINK"/> noma <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_2"/>thumela impendulo<ph name="END_LINK_2"/></translation>
<translation id="6491651957026506753">Leli fayela liyingozi, ngakho-ke i-Ecosia ilivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="1851101453239911251"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD"/>Indlela esisebenzisa ngayo le datha:<ph name="END_BOLD"/> Amasayithi angagcina ulwazi nge-Ecosia mayelana nezintshisekelo zakho. Ngokwesibonelo, uma uvakashela isayithi ukuze uthenge izicathulo zomjaho webanga elide, isayithi lingachaza intshisekelo yakho njengokugijima umjaho. Kamuva, uma uvakashela isayithi elihlukile ukuze ubhalisele umjaho, lelo sayithi lingakubonisa isikhangiso sezicathulo zokugijima ezisekelwe kuzintshisekelo zakho.</translation>
