<translation id="592990842052138727">I-EcosiaOS ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngoba imininingwane yokungena ngemvume kwe-akhawunti yakho akusisesikhathini.</translation>
<translation id="665177868576952817">Ukuze uthumele inombolo kusukela lapha kufoni yakho ye-Android, ngena ngemvume ku-Ecosia kuwo womabili amadivayisi.</translation>
<translation id="4070480171055648632">I-akhawunti yakho iphethwe i-<ph name="MANAGER_NAME"/>. Umlawuli wakho angabona futhi ahlele le phrofayela yebhrawuza ye-Ecosia nedatha yayo efana namabhukhimakhi, umlando, namaphasiwedi.</translation>
<translation id="1025044809499013222">Isibuyekezo esibalulekile sokuvikela se-Ecosia sisanda kusetshenziswa. Qalisa kabusha manje bese sizobuyisela amathebhu akho.</translation>
<translation id="7864624828358709494">I-Ecosia ivimbele leli fayela ngoba linohlelo olungayilungele ikhompuyutha</translation>
<translation id="3816260943154642689">Izintshisekelo zakho njengoba zilinganiselwe yi-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8023973672752791660">Umyalo wokubophezeleka ngaphakathi kwe-beta ye-Ecosia ukuze kuvunyelwe ithrafikhi ye-mDNS.</translation>
<translation id="4811228173434336381">Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8550334526674375523">Le phrofayela yomsebenzi ihluke ngokugcwele kusukela kuphrofayela yakho siqu.</translation>
<translation id="7185777478310554774">Kukhona inguqulo entsha ye-Ecosia etholakalayo, futhi ishesha kakhulu kunakuqala.</translation>
<translation id="5622136942112821750">Ngamaphrofayela we-Ecosia ungahlukanisa zonke izinto zakho ze-Ecosia. Lokhu kwenza kube lula ukuhlukanisa phakathi komsebenzi nokuzijabulisa.</translation>
<translation id="18064594488616674">I-Ecosia ayiphenduli. Qalisa kabusha manje?</translation>
<translation id="6896860023874996542">I-Ecosia idinga imvume yokufinyelela kwikhamera yakho ukudala imephu engu-3D yendawo yakho ekuzungezile</translation>
<translation id="7558678848273505235">{0,plural, =1{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha kuminithi elingu-1}one{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha kumaminithi angu-#}other{I-Ecosia izoqalisa kabusha kumaminithi angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="8641606876632989680">I-Chrome izokwazisa uma ungena ngemvume ngephasiwedi eyonakalisiwe</translation>
<translation id="8649026945479135076">Kujwayelekile ukuthi amasayithi owavakashelayo akhumbule izinto onentshisekelo kuzo, enze ukuzizwela kube ngokwezifiso. Amasayithi angagcina nolwazi nge-Chrome mayelana nezintshisekelo zakho.</translation>
<translation id="9090890391337853620">Isisizi se-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="524314285625975879">Iphinda ilawule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswayo uma uqala i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="4997668724897475215">I-Ecosia incoma ukuskena leli fayela ngenxa yokuthi kungenzeka ukuthi liyingozi</translation>
<translation id="4170280082681554565">Ngamaphrofayela we-Ecosia ungahlukanisa zonke izinto zakho ze-Ecosia. Dala amaphrofayela wabangane nomndeni, noma uhlukanise phakathi komsebenzi nobumnandi.</translation>
<translation id="8712767363896337380">Cishe isisesikhathini! Qalisa kabusha i-Chrome ukuqedela ukubuyekeza.</translation>
<translation id="873133009373065397">I-Google Chrome ayikwazi ukunquma noma isethe isiphequluli esizenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="1975037445584526511">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-Ecosia, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 7.</translation>
<translation id="2695952268686253864">I-Ecosia ingaphandle kwedethi</translation>
<translation id="8825634023950448068">Ukuze sivikele ubumfihlo bakho, sisula ngokuzenzakalelayo izintshisekelo zakho ezindala kunamaviki ama-4. Njengoba uqhubeka nokubhrawuza, intshisekelo ingase ivele ohlwini futhi. Futhi uma i-Chrome ikuthola kungalungile noma ungafuni ukubona izikhangiso ezithile, ungayisusa intshisekelo.</translation>
<translation id="5066194399237265772">I-Ecosia izama ukuhlela amaphasiwedi. Thayipha amaphasiwedi akho e-Windows ukuze uvumele lokhu.</translation>
<translation id="6078545897140861225">Iphinda ilawule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswayo uma uqala i-Ecosia noma uchofoza kunkinobho ye-Ikhaya.</translation>
<translation id="1401515072108809622">I-Ecosia ayisebenzi</translation>
<translation id="8862326446509486874">Awunawo amalungelo afanele wokufakwa okukuleveli yesistimu. Zama ukuqalisa isifaki futhi njengomlawuli.</translation>
<translation id="8282620071565190081">Phinda uqalise i-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="7849498640944199147">Ukuze uthumele inombolo kusukela ku-<ph name="ORIGIN"/> kufoni yakho ye-Android, ngena ngemvume ku-Ecosia kuwo womabili amadivayisi.</translation>
<translation id="7910693244647744044">Uvule Ukuphequlula Ngokuphepha Okugqamile ku-akhawunti yakho. Manje yitholele i-Ecosia.</translation>
<translation id="8986207147630327271">Ungeza iphrofayela yomsebenzi kulesi siphequluli futhi unikeza umlawuli wakho ulawulo olungaphezulu nje kwephrofayela yomsebenzi.</translation>
<translation id="8989968390305463310">Umlando wakho wokubhrawuza uthinta izikhangiso ozibonayo kanye nezinto ozishisakalelayo njengoba kulinganiselwa ngezansi. Ukuze ivikele ubumfihlo bakho, i-Chrome isula ngokuzenzakalelayo izintshisekelo zakho njalo ngenyanga. Izintshisekelo zingavuseleleka ngaphandle kwalapho uma uzisusa.</translation>
<translation id="7348818664647668234">{0,plural, =0{Isibuyekezo se-Ecosia siyatholakala}=1{Isibuyekezo se-Ecosia siyatholakala}one{Isibuyekezo se-Ecosia sitholakale izinsuku ezingu-#}other{Isibuyekezo se-Ecosia sitholakale izinsuku ezingu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="9003498785844995646">Uma ivuliwe, i-Chrome igcina amandla ebhethri ngokukhawulela umsebenzi ongemuva nemiphumela ebonakalayo, njengokuskrola okubushelelezi namazinga ozimele wevidiyo. <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>Funda kabanzi<ph name="END_LINK"/> noma <ph name="BEGIN_LINK_2"/>thumela impendulo<ph name="END_LINK_2"/></translation>
<translation id="9047384314208087523">Isistimu ye-EcosiaOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="5675757883980078189">I-Ecosia idinga i-Windows 7 noma ngaphezulu.</translation>
<translation id="911206726377975832">Phinda ususe idatha yakho yokudlulisa amehlo?</translation>
<translation id="9138603949443464873">Ukuze ufake izinguquko zaho, qalisa kabusha i-Chrome</translation>
<translation id="9195993889682885387">I-Chrome ingasikisela izinto ozithakaselayo ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wokubhrawuza kusukela emavikini ambalwa adlule. Lolu lwazi luhlala kudivayisi yakho.</translation>
<translation id="5704599732514791330">Buyekeza i-Ecosia ukuze uqale ukuvumelanisa</translation>
<translation id="838842459108103907">Yenza i-Ecosia ngokwezifiso</translation>
<translation id="3070276123152913305">Qala kabusha i-EcosiaOS Flex</translation>
<translation id="4512092435423703529">Ukuze ufinyelele ezintweni zakho ze-Ecosia kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho, ngena ngemvume, bese uvula ukuvumelanisa.</translation>
<translation id="7972668220031382654">I-Ecosia incoma ukuskena leli fayela ngenxa yokuthi kungenzeka ukuthi liyingozi.</translation>
